{"tid":2290234,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"同樣係廢佬行為，識字同唔識字可以爭好遠","createTime":"2020-11-18T01:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T01:09:00.000Z","uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed30417582132eed1cc70d17467a79f9a04c1f6d","tid":2290234,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:07:40.000Z","msg":"「自余為僇人，居是州，恆惴慄。<br />\n    其隙也，則施施而行，漫漫而遊。<br />\n    日與其徒上高山，入深林，窮迴谿，幽泉怪石，無遠不到；<br />\n    到則披草而坐，傾壺而醉；<br />\n    醉則更相枕以臥，臥而夢，意有所極，夢亦同趣；<br />\n    覺而起，起而歸。<br />\n    以為凡是州之山水有異態者，皆我有也，而未始知西山之怪特。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuS2H43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuS2H43.jpg&h=1efff313&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a66bd7ea8f07ca43c35b538bee73cf265efa092","tid":2290234,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}